I have been in kolkata for few years ..before moving..I read about the place and culture.. one line stuck in my mind was that bengali is the sweetest of the languages.. and i felt it to be true.. even when my manager is angry and scolds..it doesn't sound harsh rather soft...

When the anger even sounds soft... This song..the bangla lyrics is just soothing and nostalgic with music..

Btw I dont understand bengali..
